# Issue 4 (Oracle Connection Reset)

Earlier in the log you have

```
ORA-17002
Connection reset
```

followed by

```
HikariPool-1 - Start completed
```

and Hibernate successfully executes DDL afterwards.

That means Oracle connectivity recovered, so this is **not the startup failure**. It may indicate a transient network issue, SCAN listener redirection, or load balancing, but it is not the reason the application exits. 

